{"tid":854111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗將乘高鐵訪福建：我要親自支持偉大高鐵","createTime":"2018-10-09T06:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T08:41:34.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2fbe9b143f1bd745ccc6d77eac5c5cb32507f747","tid":854111,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://linepost.hk/images/cheunhkin.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flinepost.hk%2Fimages%2Fcheunhkin.jpg&h=493d7164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗出席香港福建經貿合作推介會致詞時說，廣深港高鐵上月23日開通後，港人到福州廈門等地旅遊或工幹變得方便，他下月27至29日將首度率領政府代表團乘坐高鐵訪問福州，「以親自支持這個偉大的高鐵」，並共同主持兩地第三次合作會議。<br />\n<br />\n他說，今日兩地將於合作儀式上簽署30份協議，為福建與本港合作注入新動力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://linepost.hk/index.php/news/4496-d20181009-3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flinepost.hk%2Findex.php%2Fnews%2F4496-d20181009-3&d=lb9mAeaxn1WEdioOs5bZismB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=292d3823\" target=\"_blank\">http://linepost.hk/index.php/news/4496-d20181009-3</a>"},{"pid":"57711bb5e1301a638a371f10bc6d0d05e6fdc0b7","tid":854111,"uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"一路好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95358619a87e77a6de128d1b4c91890624855f22","tid":854111,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:47:04.000Z","msg":"習氏創建高鐵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f199289a814e858fb60a1d8ccd7c9c704c3e5b6","tid":854111,"uid":71768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d047980579a91b789207edb25100df55da8850","tid":854111,"uid":38982,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:47:54.000Z","msg":"走左唔好返黎<img src